WEBVTT

00:00:00.110 --> 00:00:08.109
Rapid growth in the number of Jehovah's Witnesses calls for expansion of many of the branches worldwide.

00:00:08.109 --> 00:00:10.109
How are they financed?

00:00:10.109 --> 00:00:18.109
All expenses are met by voluntary donations, no dues, tithes or collections.

00:00:18.109 --> 00:00:25.109
Following the Bible principle, each one contributes as he has resolved in his heart.
